## 🆕 Newly Added Modules

### CV Management
- `GET /api/cv` - list current user CVs
- `POST /api/cv` - create CV
- `PUT /api/cv/:id` - update CV
- `DELETE /api/cv/:id` - delete CV

### Interview Scheduling
- `GET /api/interviews` - list interviews with RBAC visibility
- `POST /api/interviews` - schedule interview for an application
- `PUT /api/interviews/:id` - update interview
- `DELETE /api/interviews/:id` - delete interview

### API Documentation
- OpenAPI endpoint: `GET /api/openapi`
- Swagger UI page: `GET /api-docs`
